strip directory and suffix from filenames

##) SYNOPSIS:
```sh basename path```
strip directory and suffix from filenames

##) EXAMPLES:

```sh basename /usr/bin/sort```
    "sort"

```sh basename include/stdio.h .h```
    "stdio"

```sh basename -s .h include/stdio.h```
    "stdio"

```sh basename -a any/str1 any/str2```
    "str1" followed by "str2